{"tid":1411050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手推]好心其他記者以後讓個位比利君雅問","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:44:45.000Z","uid":249718,"like":150,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3275695017c76460f3bbaf4bc80c00cf65b7796b","tid":1411050,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:53:05.000Z","msg":"政府記者會根本得記者問答環節係有價值<br />\n英文班記者講廢話 比林鄭講兩句遊下花園就無問<br />\n根本係無撚用 全部係啲毫無價值嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n記者同行 中文報嘅特別係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你地讓個位俾利君雅啦</span></span></span><br />\n依家擺到明班狗官突登避佢啊<br />\n你讓個位俾佢問啲有價值入肉嘅問題好無？<br />\n利君雅每次問完問題都係振奮人心 完全係核彈級咁打落政府到<br />\n比佢問起碼比到某部分市民睇清政府啦<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">85三罷<br />\n七區集會等陣見！！！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"a013491422db7a0bb412a0446f5ce6962680c513","tid":1411050,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d5b9b28b95dceb2b5ed9c26b229aed12e10f09c","tid":1411050,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e52102028b11e480feecbbd0b41fb9e46af7ff8","tid":1411050,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e9d887925722395afd7694fc8ce26cf666e8a2b","tid":1411050,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"每一次都讓咪!"},{"pid":"273e5d635155b36aed22945c75520157fe75e028","tid":1411050,"uid":271756,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:54:26.000Z","msg":"完全認同起碼第一題要讓俾香港記者之首利君雅"},{"pid":"cbdce694b5346e53b207973059445bfb130fc3fb","tid":1411050,"uid":249718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"推 自推"},{"pid":"564559e38d0bf26259ed61a465c19387c60f5380","tid":14